        <span class="bio-eyebrow">About Ace Strategies</span>
        <h1 class="bio-headline">Trusted relationships. Industry specialists. Strategic communicators.</h1>
        <p class="bio-body">Ace Strategies launched in 2024 to offer an independent, personalised and responsive corporate affairs firm to the market.</p>
        <p class="bio-body">Founder Matt Neagle was intent to deliver impactful outcomes that make a difference and has built a community of specialists who are solutions driven and able to overcome complex challenges.</p>
        <p class="bio-body">Headquartered in Adelaide, we support Australian and international organisations to navigate complex political or industrial environments and regulated sectors.</p>
        <p class="bio-body">From global markets to local communities, and the corridors of Australian parliament, our work is grounded in the belief that integrity, approachability, and a sincere willingness to serve are the prerequisites for success.</p>
